race.description: Penneshaw Pub Kangaroo Island Cup Ht2 Handicap
race.comment: ROYAL FOX (1) improved sharply over 1600m at Morphettville three weeks ago, getting home by a head. Has the talent to build on that fine effort last start. THERMODYNAMIC (2) missed the placings two runs back then improved last start but found one better over 1800m at Morphettville. Faces an easier assignment so he is likely to play a big role. EAGLELOU (5) has been out of the winner's list for a long time, last start finishing fifth at Gawler over 2108m. On his best form he is one of the chief contenders. FOOTPRINTS (6) looks close to a win, finishing in the placings at her last couple of runs. Should park just off the speed. Not to be discounted.
